          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-1" n="1">
              <hi rend="display-initial">B<hi rend="small-caps">EAUTY</hi> alone inspires my lay,</hi>
            </l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-2" n="2">She traces out the flow'ry way;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-3" n="3">She varies every verse I sing;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-4" n="4"><hi rend="italics">Beauty</hi>'s an unexhausted spring:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-5" n="5">For where she chuses her abode</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-6" n="6">There leads the true <hi rend="italics">Parnassian</hi> road;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-7" n="7">There his fixt seat <hi rend="italics">Apollo</hi> chuses,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-8" n="8">There without summons flock the <hi rend="italics">muses</hi>:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-9" n="9">Inspir'd by <hi rend="italics">Beauty</hi> I presume</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-10" n="10">To sing the <hi rend="italics">Lady's Dressing-Room</hi>:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-11" n="11">No <hi rend="italics">formal order</hi> here is found,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-12" n="12">But <hi rend="italics">gay confusion</hi> strows the ground:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-13" n="13">A <hi rend="italics">shop</hi> of millenary wares:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-14" n="14">A <hi rend="italics">Magazine</hi> of female airs;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-15" n="15">What hands can shape or heads produce,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-16" n="16">All modes, or in or out of use:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-17" n="17">But what you saw, O <hi rend="italics">Muse</hi>, rehearse,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-18" n="18">And sing a <hi rend="italics">Catalogue</hi> in <hi rend="italics">verse</hi>.</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-19" n="19">A <hi rend="italics">fan</hi>, that many a mounting cost;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-20" n="20">An <hi rend="italics">equipage</hi>--- the trinkets-- lost:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-21" n="21">A <hi rend="italics">feather</hi>, late a shining flow'r;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-22" n="22">A <hi rend="italics">watch</hi> that never minds the hour:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-23" n="23">A <hi rend="italics">busk</hi> long us'd to bear the yoke;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-24" n="24">A <hi rend="italics">crosiatt</hi>, from the necklace broke:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-25" n="25">A <hi rend="italics">shell</hi>, retentive once of <hi rend="italics">snuff</hi>:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-26" n="26">A <hi rend="italics">case</hi> once master of a <hi rend="italics">muff</hi>:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-27" n="27">A <hi rend="italics">mantile</hi>, that has lost a wing;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-28" n="28">A <hi rend="italics">cawl</hi>, with disobedient string:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-29" n="29">Far from its <hi rend="italics">head</hi> a <hi rend="italics">wire</hi> mislaid;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-30" n="30">A <hi rend="italics">slipper</hi> from its fellow stray'd:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-31" n="31">Here <hi rend="italics">knots</hi>, that can no longer kill;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-32" n="32">There <hi rend="italics">lappets</hi>, learning to lie still:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-33" n="33">Here <hi rend="italics">aprons</hi> throwing off their <hi rend="italics">fringes</hi>,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-34" n="34">There <hi rend="italics">boxes</hi> flying from their <hi rend="italics">binges</hi>:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-35" n="35">Worn <hi rend="italics">petticoats</hi> lost <hi rend="italics">mantuas</hi> mourning;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-36" n="36"><hi rend="italics">Full dresses</hi> into <hi rend="italics">night-gowns</hi> turning:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-37" n="37"><hi rend="italics">Tuckers</hi> to <hi rend="italics">pinners</hi> lending <hi rend="italics">laces</hi>,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-38" n="38">And <hi rend="italics">breadths</hi>, like <hi rend="italics">statesmen</hi>, changing <hi rend="italics">places</hi>.</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-39" n="39">A <hi rend="italics">girdle</hi> o'er its <hi rend="italics">buckle</hi> bound,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-40" n="40">Wrapt like a snake in its own round:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-41" n="41">A <hi rend="italics">hood</hi>, long pleas'd with graceful pride,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-42" n="42">To shew the face it seem'd to hide:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-43" n="43">A <hi rend="italics">quilting-frame</hi>, long doom'd to stand,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-44" n="44">Or freed by <hi rend="italics">Nelly</hi>'s aiding hand:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-45" n="45">Here shatter'd <hi rend="italics">hoops</hi> of plyant cane</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-46" n="46">Exil'd from their <hi rend="italics">Elysian</hi> reign:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-47" n="47">There <hi rend="italics">ribs</hi> of <hi rend="italics">Whale</hi>, by time decay'd</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-48" n="48">(Proud of the shape they took) not made:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-49" n="49">A <hi rend="italics">ring</hi>, with <hi rend="italics">motto</hi> out of date,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-50" n="50">Sad prospect of its giver's fate:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-51" n="51">A <hi rend="italics">breast-knot</hi> late a dangerous snare,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-52" n="52">That bids of faded charms beware:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-53" n="53">A <hi rend="italics">net</hi>, no longer laid for hearts,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-54" n="54">A <hi rend="italics">parrot</hi>, of less pleasing parts:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-55" n="55">A <hi rend="italics">dog</hi>, not stroak'd with wonted care,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-56" n="56">For all his growth of toupeed hair:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-57" n="57">A <hi rend="italics">monkey</hi> chain'd to good behaviour;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-58" n="58">Tho' now and then receiv'd in favour:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-59" n="59">A <hi rend="italics">cage</hi>, its little inmate flown;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-60" n="60">Hence warn'd, securely guard your own:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-61" n="61">The <hi rend="italics">story</hi> of a maid <hi rend="italics">undone</hi>,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-62" n="62">Sweet ruin! taught by others, shun:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-63" n="63">A <hi rend="italics">sermon</hi> never to be read;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-64" n="64">They need no guide who cautious tread.</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-65" n="65">T<hi rend="small-caps">HE</hi> <hi rend="italics">toilette</hi> here not laid in state</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-66" n="66">Scarce half employs the hands that wait,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-67" n="67">And to the fair small aid imparts,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-68" n="68">Ill furnish'd with <hi rend="italics">cosmetic</hi> arts:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-69" n="69">Here no false <hi rend="italics">flatt'ring glass</hi> is fixt;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-70" n="70">Here no <hi rend="italics">Camelion water</hi> mixt;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-71" n="71">No <hi rend="italics">paste</hi> with plastic labour spread;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-72" n="72">No <hi rend="italics">furrow</hi> smooth'd with <hi rend="italics">level lead</hi>;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-73" n="73">And how cou'd <hi rend="italics">cheeks</hi> of <hi rend="italics">Spanish dye</hi></l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-74" n="74">With <hi rend="italics">nature</hi>'s purer <hi rend="italics">roses</hi> vye?</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-75" n="75">How the sick <hi rend="italics">pale</hi> of <hi rend="italics">Bismute</hi> show</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-76" n="76">With hands more white than feather'd snow?</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-77" n="77">What envious <hi rend="italics">breath</hi> of faint <hi rend="italics">perfume</hi></l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-78" n="78">Can copy <hi rend="italics">health</hi>'s sweet flow'ry bloom?</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-79" n="79">What <hi rend="italics">mimick Tinge</hi> of <hi rend="italics">ruby</hi> hue</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-80" n="80">Supply the <hi rend="italics">lips ambrosial</hi> dew?</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-81" n="81">None here the <hi rend="italics">chymic oil</hi> prepare</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-82" n="82">To give a gloss to chesnut hair:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-83" n="83">Or nightly <hi rend="italics">traps</hi> insiduous lay,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-84" n="84">To catch <hi rend="italics">new eye-brows</hi> for the day.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-85" n="85">Vain arts! that in slight fetters hold,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-86" n="86">And left to the deform'd and old;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-87" n="87">Who, destitute of native arms</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-88" n="88">Attempt to wound with borrow'd charms.</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-89" n="89">L<hi rend="small-caps">ET</hi> no rich <hi rend="italics">jar</hi> adorn <hi rend="italics">this room</hi>,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-90" n="90">No <hi rend="italics">carpet</hi> wrought in <hi rend="italics">Persian</hi> loom,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-91" n="91">No <hi rend="italics">branch</hi> from <hi rend="italics">figur'd cieling</hi> fall;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-92" n="92">No <hi rend="italics">Belgic tap'stry</hi> cloath the wall:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-93" n="93">Hang here no piece of <hi rend="italics">roman</hi> hand,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-94" n="94">Here let no <hi rend="italics">Grecian sculpture</hi> stand;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-95" n="95"><hi rend="italics">Diana</hi> bathing tho' it be,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-96" n="96">Or <hi rend="italics">Venus</hi> rising from the sea:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-97" n="97">Where <hi rend="italics">art</hi> and <hi rend="italics">nature</hi> seem at strife,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-98" n="98">No <hi rend="italics">image</hi> truly equals <hi rend="italics">life</hi>;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-99" n="99">And who by folly not betray'd</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-100" n="100">Wou'd quit the <hi rend="italics">substance</hi> for the <hi rend="italics">shade</hi>?</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-101" n="101">Where <hi rend="italics">beauty</hi> condescends to reign</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z386T163-line-102" n="102">All other <hi rend="italics">ornaments</hi> are vain.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
      </div>
